The '''Janzur Museum''' (also known as the '''Janzour Museum''') is an [[archaeological museum]] located in [[Janzur]], [[Libya]].<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.temehu.com/Cities_sites/museum-of-janzur.htm |title = Janzur Museum | publisher = Temehu Tourism Services}}</ref> The museum showcases a funerary complex that is still under excavation by the Archaeology Department in Tripoli.
